const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What’s included in a deep cleaning service?",
    answer: "Our Deep Cleaning Service goes beyond routine upkeep to give your home a complete reset. It includes:\n\n• Kitchen: Degreasing and sanitizing countertops, sinks, appliance exteriors, cabinet fronts, and stovetops.\n• Bathrooms: Scrubbing and disinfecting toilets, tubs, showers, sinks, mirrors, and tile.\n• Living Areas & Bedrooms: Detailed dusting of furniture, baseboards, vents, blinds, and ceiling fans; vacuuming and mopping all floors.\n• Hard-to-Reach Areas: Cleaning behind furniture (when accessible), polishing fixtures, and addressing areas often overlooked during regular cleaning.\n\nThis service is ideal for seasonal cleanings, move-in/move-out situations, or anytime your home needs a top-to-bottom refresh."
